Package net.jqwik.time.api.constraints

Annotationsschnittstelle SecondRange

@Target({ANNOTATION_TYPE,PARAMETER,TYPE_USE}) @Retention(RUNTIME) @Documented @API(status=EXPERIMENTAL, since="1.5.1") public @interface SecondRange
Constrain the range of generated second parameters.

Applies to LocalDateTime, Instant, OffsetDateTime, LocalTime and OffsetTime parameters which are also annotated with @ForAll.
